\id 1TI - Kaluli Bible 
\h 1 Timoti 
\toc1 Moęž‰foęž‰s Agel We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰ Timoti Emoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰ 
\toc2 1 Timoti 
\toc3 1Tim 
\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s Agel We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰  
\mt1 Timoti  
\mt2 Emoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰  
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we  
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s we Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Timoti emoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰. Timoti e Keliso kaluwoęž‰ hoęž‰gi dowakiyoęž‰, Foęž‰l oęž‰liaęž‰ nanog diaęž‰li siaęž‰len. (Iligaęž‰feloęž‰ Kalu 16.1-3) Timoti e Aęž‰fesaęž‰s saęž‰s aęž‰na dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ saęž‰s aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰ki, to we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s us aęž‰namioęž‰, to otalen daęž‰labiki saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Nowoęž‰, hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ man koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ widakiyoęž‰ saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰ mogagilab koęž‰loęž‰, Timoti eyoęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰ki, to we hagugaki saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.  
\ip Nowoęž‰ saęž‰sdoęž‰ dinafa boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ saęž‰s amiloęž‰ misaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale dibebeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ daęž‰feakiyoęž‰, man ililoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰.  
\ip Nowoęž‰ Timoti e Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ nanog dian kalu nafale domaęž‰ki saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ eloęž‰ tili dofoęž‰likiloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Ne Foęž‰l, Yaęž‰su Keliso eloęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ ne. Gode niloęž‰ asuwaęž‰takiloęž‰ gasili aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰, nililoęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ yasisoęž‰l Yaęž‰su Keliso, aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ne daęž‰feyoęž‰.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1.2 \xt Ilig 16.1-3, Tait 1.4\x*Timoti, ge hendele tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰ ni soęž‰wale oęž‰ngoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we gemoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l. Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ nili Misaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ini kanuloęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ nofolan oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰saloęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ dofoęž‰meleaęž‰ki, to we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l.   
\s1 To halaboęž‰ walamaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰liki hagugu sioęž‰  
\p
\v 3 Ne Masedonia hena haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, ge Aęž‰fesaęž‰s aęž‰naka oęž‰meleaęž‰ki, gemoęž‰woęž‰ towoęž‰ salifoęž‰gane koęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ niyoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ waęž‰ka saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Ge Aęž‰fesaęž‰s aęž‰na silikiyoęž‰, kalu nolbaęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ man kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰loęž‰ hala widaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰fomaęž‰ki, giyoęž‰ towoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lubi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1.4 \xt 1Tim 4.7, Tait 1.14\x*Iliyoęž‰ kandayoęž‰ malolaęž‰sen oęž‰liaęž‰ e maęž‰mu i mioęž‰ agelaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ nenelaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ widalikiyoęž‰, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ walaęž‰soęž‰bokaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki, imoęž‰woęž‰ halale saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Moęž‰woęž‰ iyoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ malolaęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, gadiaki kegaęž‰melaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ nanog diab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib. Kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰maęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene nanogoęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib.  
\v 5 Niloęž‰ gemoęž‰loęž‰ dimidamaęž‰kiloęž‰ to soęž‰loęž‰loęž‰ we. Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ egeleboęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ widaęž‰bi. Man aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, asuloęž‰woęž‰ goęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ dowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, hala dimidoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰asulaki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabu hendele dowalikiyoęž‰, haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰, aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib.  
\v 6 Kalu noloęž‰ man widaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰ haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, madali to saęž‰laęž‰lab.  
\v 7 Iyoęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ eleloęž‰ widan kalu domaęž‰noęž‰ asulaki widaęž‰lab koęž‰sega, to inidoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ to ililoęž‰ halale widab oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ ininoęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰fanda asuloęž‰.   
\p
\v 8 \x - \xo 1.8 \xt Lom 7.12,16\x*Koęž‰sega kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰ ele difaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ digaloęž‰le widalega, nioęž‰ ele aęž‰noęž‰ nafa dowab aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰l.  
\v 9-10 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ele aęž‰noęž‰, digaloęž‰ kalu aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰, moęž‰saefaęž‰. Koęž‰sega ele difaęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰saęž‰lab kalu aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰iyaboęž‰, Godeyoęž‰ gola baęž‰daboęž‰, mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰senoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aumboęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰, henfeloęž‰ mandoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰laboęž‰, ene iya anoloęž‰ sana sowaboęž‰, kalu noldoęž‰ sana sowaęž‰laboęž‰, uwoęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰laboęž‰, daęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰laboęž‰, kalu noloęž‰ afale tilili haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ madali nanog dian kalu taęž‰felaboęž‰, doęž‰loęž‰le saęž‰lakiloęž‰ dikili saęž‰laboęž‰, moęž‰walilab amioęž‰ towaęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lanoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ man digaloęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, ele saefaęž‰ we i aęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab.  
\v 11 Man digaloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to nafale aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ imiloęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ nemoęž‰ walamaęž‰ki widoęž‰. To nafa aęž‰noęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰loęž‰ Gode Alan koęž‰loęž‰ wabulu saęž‰laęž‰lab aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰.   
\s1 Gode eyoęž‰ Foęž‰l e nofoloęž‰ alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰  
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 1.12 \xt Ilig 9.15, 1Kol 15.9-10, Gala 1.15-16\x*Nili Alan, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰yoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ dimi koęž‰loęž‰ niyoęž‰ emoęž‰woęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l. Eyoęž‰ ne dibebeaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, niyoęž‰ nanog aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li ditandalemaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰asulaki, ene nanog dimaęž‰ki daęž‰fe alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ emoęž‰woęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1.13 \xt Ilig 8.3, 9.1-5\x*Tamin amioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ dioęž‰ge saęž‰laki, e oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis dowaęž‰liki, e niyoęž‰ mogagilaęž‰len. Koęž‰sega ne e moęž‰fanda asulaki moęž‰ tilidabu iliki, aęž‰na dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ eyoęž‰ ne nofoloęž‰ alifaęž‰.  
\v 14 Nili Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰yoęž‰, ene kanulan man aęž‰noęž‰ ne amioęž‰ mada modoęž‰ koęž‰goęž‰laki, ene tilidabu oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ nemoęž‰ dimi.   
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 1.15 \xt Luk 19.10\x*To we hendele saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰bi. â€śYaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ gasiliaęž‰niki, henfeloęž‰ wena mioęž‰,â€ť niyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ne mada mogagoęž‰leloęž‰ dimidaęž‰len kaluwoęž‰ ne.  
\v 16 Koęž‰sega Gode eyoęž‰ ne nofolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰saloęž‰ domaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ nemoęž‰ koęž‰le widoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tambo aęž‰noęž‰ asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, iyoęž‰loęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso amioęž‰ tilidaęž‰daki, koęž‰ngoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ dimaęž‰kiyoęž‰, mogagoęž‰le kalu nemoęž‰ koęž‰le widoęž‰.  
\v 17 Gode mada oęž‰m,  
\q1 Koęž‰ngoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ misaęž‰yoęž‰ E.  
\q1 Moęž‰sowanoęž‰ E.  
\q1 Siyaęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰danoęž‰ E.  
\q1 Godeyoęž‰ imilise E koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.  
\q1 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ E mada nafale aęž‰laęž‰liki,  
\q2 Ene wiyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo wabulu saęž‰laęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰ib.  
\q1 Hendele.   
\p
\v 18 Ni soęž‰wa Timoti, tamin amiloęž‰ saęž‰s misaęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ gemoęž‰loęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, niyoęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ to oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰ wala saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. To aęž‰noęž‰ ge asulufoęž‰liki kudu haęž‰naki, ge halaledoęž‰ buban kaluwoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dotaęž‰gaęž‰, nanogoęž‰ aęž‰na halale dimidaęž‰bi.  
\v 19 Goęž‰noęž‰n tilidabuwoęž‰ halale taęž‰li siliki, man digaloęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dinafa alobaęž‰daki, nanogoęž‰ aęž‰na dimidaęž‰bi. Moęž‰woęž‰ kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, inin tilidabuwoęž‰ hoęž‰n koęž‰su koęž‰loęž‰ u nowa basayakiloęž‰ mogagan oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaęž‰lab.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1.20 \xt 1Kol 5.5, 2Tim 4.14-15\x*Kalu aęž‰laęž‰ nowoęž‰, Himeneus oęž‰liaęž‰ Alegsanda oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ moęž‰mogagimaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulaki, niyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yaęž‰ dagiya difaęž‰.   
\c 2  
\s1 Dulugu saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ manoęž‰ widoęž‰  
\p
\v 1 Tamin amioęž‰, gioęž‰ Godemoęž‰ koęž‰le dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tambo asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰ halale alifomaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰ to saęž‰laęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 2 Giliyoęž‰ gamani misaęž‰ kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ gamaniloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu noloęž‰loęž‰, Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi. Nililoęž‰ i koęž‰loęž‰ dulugu saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ sagalaęž‰liki haęž‰sa mesaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki goęž‰l. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ niliyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ wabudaęž‰liki, eloęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki goęž‰l.  
\v 3 Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ gab aęž‰noęž‰ mada nafale koęž‰loęž‰, Gode niloęž‰ gasili oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ sagale alifaęž‰ib.  
\v 4 Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tambo aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasiliaęž‰noęž‰ asulab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tambo to hendeleyoęž‰ mada tili asulumaęž‰ki asulab.  
\v 5 Moęž‰woęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ imilig koęž‰loęž‰lab, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰ us amiloęž‰ aęž‰lab kaluleyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso, imilig e koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2.6 \xt Lom 3.29-30, Gala 1.4\x*Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tambo gaęž‰li meseaęž‰ki, su dimian aumboęž‰ Yaęž‰su eyoęž‰ enenoęž‰ boba dimi. Man aęž‰noęž‰ ene hoęž‰lendeya faęž‰laęž‰dowaki, Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tambo aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasiliaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰li widoęž‰.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2.7 \xt Ilig 9.15, Gala 2.7-8, 2Tim 1.11\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to walamaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ne Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ ne daęž‰feaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalema sab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ tilidabu hendeleyoęž‰ walamaęž‰kiloęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ ne. Niyoęž‰ to we moęž‰dikidaki, hendele soęž‰loęž‰l.   
\p
\v 8 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ niloęž‰ asulaboęž‰ we. Henoęž‰ tambo amioęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ ene dagiyoęž‰ dulugufoęž‰liki, ene melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dimiaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, gadianoęž‰ aundoęž‰ma aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to keganoęž‰ aundoęž‰ma iliki, Godemoęž‰woęž‰ towoęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰laęž‰lubi. \fig Dagiyoęž‰ dulugufoęž‰liki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi.|alt="Lifting holy hands in prayer" src="19_Ps_52_01_RG_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© Sweet Publishing http://sweetpublishing.com, licensed under a CC: BY-SA 3.0 Unported licence." ref="2.8" \fig*   
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 2.9 \xt 1Bid 3.3-5\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kaęž‰isale iyoęž‰ soęž‰goęž‰ saęž‰gaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, kalu meselemaęž‰kiyoęž‰ saęž‰gaęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo. Iyoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ sendeakiyoęž‰ misaęž‰ foęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰soęž‰bo, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ amioęž‰ soęž‰g mole alanaęž‰loęž‰ dian oęž‰liaęž‰ momadan kelegoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ goęž‰l amiloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2.10 \xt 1Tim 5.10\x*Koęž‰sega kaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ ne Godeyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ wabudaęž‰sen aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, man nafale dimidab aęž‰noęž‰, momadoęž‰ ililoęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰m.  
\v 11 Iyoęž‰ towoęž‰ moęž‰tolaki haęž‰ga iliki, Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ aęž‰na daęž‰daęž‰lubi.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2.12 \xt 1Kol 14.34\x*Kaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰ sanamaęž‰kiyoęž‰ moęž‰asuloęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ kalu siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ moęž‰walamaęž‰ki asuloęž‰l. Iyoęž‰ helaęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ meseaęž‰ki asulab.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2.13 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 2.7,21-22, 1Kol 11.8-9\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ Adam e tamindeya dimidaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Ifoęž‰ tifa dimidoęž‰.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2.14 \xt 2Kol 11.3, Gala 3.1-6\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Adam eyoęž‰ dikili sioęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰tilidabu. If eyoęž‰ dikili saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, ele difaęž‰yoęž‰ e mogasoęž‰.  
\v 15 Koęž‰sega kaęž‰isale iyoęž‰ soęž‰wayoęž‰ oęž‰li saęž‰laęž‰lian koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo i amioęž‰ egaki, iyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su amioęž‰ tilidabu iliki, kalukaęž‰isale nolboęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki, man digaloęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lalega, Gode eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasiliaęž‰ib.   
\c 3  
\s1 Saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰ manoęž‰ we  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 3.1 \xt Ilig 20.28\x*To we hendele saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Kalu abeyoęž‰ e saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu domaęž‰noęž‰ asulalega, e nanog nafale aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰ asulab.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3.2 \xt Tait 1.6-9\x*Saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ man dimidanoęž‰ we. Eyoęž‰ manoęž‰ digaloęž‰le kudu haęž‰naki, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ e hala dimidab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰asulaęž‰sen. E gayoęž‰ imilig di. E haęž‰sa dowan. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ dinafa tilidowan. E magesoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ dinafa tilidowan. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ eyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ manoęž‰ nafale widan.  
\v 3 E alunaęž‰ hoęž‰n nakiyoęž‰, moęž‰noęž‰nolan kalu dowan. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰buban. E haęž‰sa dowaki, towaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰kegan. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ e moleyoęž‰ moęž‰meselan.  
\v 4 Kalu aęž‰noęž‰ ene soęž‰loęž‰woęž‰ dinafa tilidowaki, eloęž‰ saęž‰lab aumboęž‰ ene soęž‰wayoęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰ki, boęž‰foęž‰lowan.  
\v 5 Kalu abeyoęž‰ ene ga oęž‰liaęž‰ ene soęž‰wa oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dinafayoęž‰ moęž‰tilidowalega, eyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ waga tilidomaęž‰ibaęž‰le?   
\p
\v 6 Keliso hoęž‰gi dowab aęž‰noęž‰ saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ daęž‰feaęž‰soęž‰bo. Moęž‰woęž‰ enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ e nafale aęž‰laęž‰asulalikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰waliloęž‰woęž‰ aumboęž‰, e moęž‰walilaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ falasilaęž‰maęž‰ib.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3.7 \xt 2Kol 8.21\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu eyoęž‰ haęž‰laęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ e digaloęž‰le kalu aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰ dowan. Aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰goęž‰lalega, e sendelo alitaliki, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yaęž‰ dafaya walamaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Digoęž‰naęž‰ manoęž‰ we  
\p
\v 8 Niloęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰l oęž‰leau, digoęž‰n iyoęž‰loęž‰ man nafale dimidaki, wiyoęž‰ nafa diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Iliyoęž‰ towaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lan. Iyoęž‰ alunaęž‰ hoęž‰noęž‰ modoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰naęž‰sen aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iyoęž‰ moleyoęž‰ alan asulakiyoęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ dikidakiyoęž‰ moęž‰afale diaęž‰sen.  
\v 9 Asuloęž‰ ililoęž‰woęž‰ goęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ dowaki, tilidabu aęž‰namioęž‰ to we hendeleloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ iliyoęž‰ tili asulaęž‰sen.  
\v 10 Tamin amioęž‰ ili manoęž‰ alobana baęž‰baęž‰ amioęž‰, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ eloęž‰ hala dimidoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰lalega, e digoęž‰n nanogoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ki taęž‰taęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 3.11 \xt Tait 2.3\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ga ililoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, manoęž‰ imilig oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ka dowaki, iyoęž‰ man nafale dimidaki, wiyoęž‰ nafa diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Iyoęž‰ noloęž‰ moęž‰sadaęž‰dan. Koęž‰sega iyoęž‰ haęž‰sa dowaki, ini nanogoęž‰ tambo oęž‰li tilidowaęž‰sen oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰maęž‰ domaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 12 Digoęž‰n kalu e gayoęž‰ imilig dowaki, ene soęž‰wa oęž‰liaęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dinafaloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab kalu aęž‰maęž‰ dowan.  
\v 13 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰s nanogdoęž‰ diab kalu i aęž‰noęž‰, nanogoęž‰ nafale dialiki, ili wiyoęž‰ mada nafaleyoęž‰ aęž‰na domaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowa tilidabu aęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ kalab amioęž‰ halale saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰tagimaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Godeyaęž‰ to manoęž‰ fanda widoęž‰  
\p
\v 14-15 Ne geloęž‰ amioęž‰ boęž‰boęž‰ge miaęž‰noęž‰ asulab koęž‰sega, ne boęž‰eboęž‰ moęž‰yalega, giyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ man kudu haęž‰nan aęž‰noęž‰ asulumaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we koęž‰le saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l. Godeyaęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ we. Saęž‰soęž‰ Gode melaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, saęž‰s aęž‰noęž‰ e aikoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ iliki, to hendeleloęž‰ halale taęž‰lisaboęž‰ oęž‰m.   
\p
\v 16 \x - \xo 3.16 \xt Mak 16.19, Yoęž‰n 1.14, Kolo 1.23\x*Godeyaęž‰ ene to manoęž‰ nimoęž‰loęž‰ kalab amiloęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mada alan faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, to aęž‰noęž‰ mada hendeleyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dowoęž‰. To aęž‰noęž‰ we.  
\q1 E kalule faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiyoęž‰,  
\q2 kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ E baęž‰baęž‰.  
\q1 Man eloęž‰woęž‰ digaloęž‰le aęž‰lab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰  
\q2 Godeyaęž‰ Mamayaęž‰ widoęž‰.  
\q1 Maęž‰mulaęž‰ kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ E baęž‰baęž‰.  
\q1 Widan kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ Ene manoęž‰  
\q2 soęž‰loęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰li ane koęž‰loęž‰,  
\q1 henfeloęž‰ we tambo amioęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰  
\q2 E amioęž‰ tilidabu.  
\q1 Godeyaęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ Eya ilikiyoęž‰,  
\q2 E Hebene tililiaęž‰gane.   
\c 4  
\s1 Madali to widaboęž‰ hagugu sioęž‰  
\p
\v 1 Godeyaęž‰ Mamayaęž‰yoęž‰ fanda widakiloęž‰ to sioęž‰woęž‰ we. Elemaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma dowalikiyoęž‰, kalu noloęž‰ ene tilidabuwoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, mama mogagoęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ yoęž‰idoęž‰ to saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, mama mogagoęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ widab man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰ib.  
\v 2 Man aęž‰noęž‰ madaliloęž‰ dikidan kaluwaęž‰ widaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, ili asuloęž‰ nafaloęž‰ miaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ sana sowoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowakiyoęž‰, we mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰asulakigab.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4.3 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 9.3, Lom 14.6, 1Kol 10.30-31\x*Kalu i aęž‰maęž‰ widakiyoęž‰, gayoęž‰ diaęž‰soęž‰bo aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ noloęž‰ naęž‰soęž‰bokaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki widaęž‰lab. Koęž‰sega Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale to hendeleloęž‰ asulakiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰li maiyaęž‰ki, dimidoęž‰.  
\v 4 Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ kelegoęž‰ dimidoęž‰woęž‰ tambo nafale koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ kelegoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰liki, kelegoęž‰ imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰kaęž‰laki, tambowoęž‰ oęž‰lika diaęž‰ib.  
\v 5 Moęž‰woęž‰ gililoęž‰ Godemoęž‰loęž‰ dulugu sioęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to sioęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ oęž‰lika maiyaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 6 Giyoęž‰ to niloęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gao i nolboęž‰woęž‰ dinafa widalega, ge Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu nafale dowakigab. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, nililoęž‰ tilidabuwaęž‰ man we oęž‰liaęž‰ to nafa widab amiloęž‰ giloęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ kudu ane aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ge halaidoęž‰ dowakigab.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 4.7 \xt 1Tim 1.4\x*Giyoęž‰ kandayoęž‰ malolaęž‰sen, to haęž‰goęž‰ aundoęž‰ma dowab aęž‰noęž‰ kataęž‰taęž‰bi. Koęž‰sega giyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au domaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo asuloęž‰woęž‰ diakiyoęž‰, manoęž‰ daęž‰feaęž‰lubi.  
\v 8 Doęž‰moęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki daęž‰feakiloęž‰ dimidan aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ge haęž‰lu asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib. Koęž‰sega, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ge alan asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib. Oęž‰goęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ nafale dimiaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, tif amioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ nafale dimiaęž‰ib.  
\v 9 To aęž‰noęž‰ hendele soęž‰loęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰bi.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4.10 \xt 1Tim 2.3-4\x*Melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len. Godeyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tamboloęž‰ oęž‰li gasiliaęž‰iboęž‰ e koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ e amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰ eyoęž‰ mada gasiliaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ nioęž‰ haęž‰sa iliki, asuloęž‰woęž‰ tambo Gode melaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab emoęž‰ dimiaęž‰loęž‰l.   
\p
\v 11 To we giyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale imoęž‰woęž‰ widakiyoęž‰, iyoęž‰ mada kudu haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki widaęž‰lubi.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 4.12 \xt Tait 2.15\x*Ge saęž‰leloęž‰biki, kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ ge waęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰ndabenaęž‰ki, kaęž‰laęž‰bi. Koęž‰sega iyoęž‰ gi manoęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰kiyoęž‰, giloęž‰ to saęž‰lanoęž‰loęž‰, man giloęž‰ dimidanoęž‰loęž‰, giloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lanoęž‰loęž‰, giloęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gi asuloęž‰woęž‰ goęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ dowan aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, iliyoęž‰ kudu menaęž‰ki, giyoęž‰ digale dimidaęž‰lubi.   
\p
\v 13 Ne oęž‰semoęž‰ yalikiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ agelaęž‰ meaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo ili kufaęž‰ usoęž‰ halale alitakiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ manoęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰lubi.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 4.14 \xt 2Tim 1.6\x*Saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ gi misaęž‰ waęž‰la golofoęž‰liki, ililoęž‰ dinali saęž‰lakiloęž‰ boba dimi aęž‰noęž‰ ge di koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ giyoęž‰ gola baęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\v 15 Kalukaęž‰isale tambowaęž‰yoęž‰ gi tilidabuwoęž‰ anayaboęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰asulumaęž‰ki, ge to aęž‰noęž‰ asulaęž‰likiyoęž‰, nanog aęž‰noęž‰ halale dimidaęž‰lubi.  
\v 16 Goęž‰noęž‰n man dimidan oęž‰liaęž‰ to man widaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dinafa tilidowaki, ge man aęž‰noęž‰lekoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Moęž‰woęž‰ giyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n geloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale gi toloęž‰ daęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ tambo Gode eyoęž‰ gasiliaęž‰ib.   
\c 5  
\s1 Tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ dinafa tilidowaęž‰bi  
\p
\v 1 To giloęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalu koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ sab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰waęž‰laęž‰saęž‰ndaki, giyoęž‰ haęž‰sa iliki, goęž‰lboęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰lan au, iyoęž‰ halale domaęž‰ki saęž‰laęž‰bi. Kalu soęž‰wa aęž‰noęž‰, gaomoęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰lan au, halale domaęž‰ki saęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 2 Kaęž‰isale koęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, goęž‰moęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰lan au, saęž‰laęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kaęž‰isale soęž‰wamoęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, ge maliloęž‰ iliki, gadomoęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰lan au, saęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 3 Giliyoęž‰ ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰loęž‰ma inaęž‰liloęž‰ sab aęž‰noęž‰, dinafa tilidowaęž‰bi.  
\v 4 Koęž‰sega ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ abeyoęž‰, ene soęž‰wayoęž‰ saboęž‰lalega, oęž‰ ene unuwoęž‰ saboęž‰lalega, soęž‰wa aęž‰maęž‰loęž‰woęž‰ ini tilidabuwoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naki, iliyoęž‰ ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tili dowaęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, ini iya oęž‰liaęž‰ ano oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ nanog di amiloęž‰ waęž‰l dian aumboęž‰, i tili dowoęž‰ aęž‰namiloęž‰ waęž‰l aęž‰kililian augab koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidab man aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ sagale alitab.  
\v 5 Ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ e soęž‰loęž‰loęž‰ma inaęž‰liloęž‰ sab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ene asuloęž‰woęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dimifoęž‰liki, hoęž‰len oęž‰liaęž‰ nulu oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki, dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lab.  
\v 6 Koęž‰sega ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ abeyoęž‰ enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ sagalemaęž‰noęž‰ man koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ dimidaęž‰lalega, e sowoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ ilikigab.  
\v 7 Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ hala dimidabenaęž‰kiyoęž‰, giyoęž‰ to widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ dinafa saęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 8 Koęž‰sega kalu abeyoęž‰ ene soęž‰loęž‰leyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ a eloęž‰ taęž‰sen oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰tilidowalega, kalu we ene tilidabuwoęž‰ kataęž‰taki, ene manoęž‰ mada mogagoęž‰le dowab. Haęž‰laęž‰ kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰le wengoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimidaęž‰sen.   
\p
\v 9 Ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰s boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰ki daęž‰feakiyoęž‰, ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ we oęž‰ngoęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰li diaęž‰bi. E donayoęž‰ 60 aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰ gululaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, inaęž‰ haęž‰ga iliki moęž‰taęž‰foęž‰gane aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰li diaęž‰bi.  
\v 10 Amisaęž‰n kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ manoęž‰ nafale dimidabiloęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li diaęž‰bi. Man nafa aęž‰noęž‰ we. Ene soęž‰wayoęž‰ dinafa boęž‰foęž‰lowan. Magesoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ eyoęž‰ tilidowaęž‰sen. Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ gib amioęž‰ henaęž‰mu aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa halitaęž‰sen. Hidaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ dowab amioęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ man nafa koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ eyoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lowan. Ga aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li diaęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 11-12 Koęž‰sega ga nafa amiloęž‰ saęž‰baęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰feaęž‰soęž‰bo. Moęž‰woęž‰ e kaluwaęž‰ aęž‰dimaęž‰ki asulakiyoęž‰, asuloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Kelisowaęž‰ nanog dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulan aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ tininimaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰, ene dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰tab koęž‰loęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰walilimaęž‰ib.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 5.13 \xt 2Tes 3.11\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ga aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰fealega, iyoęž‰ boęž‰sulaki, a nowa, a nowa aęž‰laęž‰ siaęž‰liki, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ walaęž‰melaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, ililoęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ dowoęž‰ towoęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰laki, madali yoęž‰idoęž‰ towoęž‰ aęž‰na sadaęž‰daęž‰melaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 14 \x - \xo 5.14 \xt 1Kol 7.9\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ga oęž‰nafa amiloęž‰ saęž‰baęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ e kaluwoęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, soęž‰wayoęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰laęž‰laęž‰liki, ene soęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ tilidowaęž‰bi, aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰ niyoęž‰ emoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰. Iyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, nili gis kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ sendelomaęž‰noęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰samaęž‰ki goęž‰l.  
\v 15 Hendele. Ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ noloęž‰ tog nafa aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰ma taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu ane koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 16 Keliso ga dowab aęž‰maęž‰ ene soęž‰loęž‰ us amioęž‰ ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ nowoęž‰ dowalega, Keliso ga aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ e dinafa boęž‰foęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰, saęž‰s e hidaęž‰yoęž‰ alanoęž‰ moęž‰diaki, ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰loęž‰ma inaęž‰lile dowab nol aęž‰noęž‰ saęž‰s iliyoęž‰ e oęž‰li boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 17 Giliyoęž‰ saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ wabudaki, moleyoęž‰ kililiaęž‰bi. Misaęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ manoęž‰ halale widakiloęž‰ wala saęž‰lab i aęž‰noęž‰, digaloęž‰le kililiaęž‰bi.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 5.18 \xt Lo 25.4, Madi 10.10, 1Kol 9.9\x*Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ towoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śKaowaęž‰ gibaęž‰yoęž‰ daęž‰si fo aęž‰noęž‰ sebeboęž‰ hamanaęž‰ki waęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰ndaęž‰lab amioęž‰, kaowaęž‰ megoęž‰foęž‰ kalitaęž‰soęž‰bo.â€ť Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to saęž‰lanoęž‰ nowoęž‰ we, â€śNanogdoęž‰ di kalu oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰, waęž‰loęž‰ kililiaęž‰ib.â€ť   
\p
\v 19 \x - \xo 5.19 \xt 2Kol 13.1\x*Saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, kalu aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ oęž‰ otalenoęž‰loęž‰ to imiligoęž‰ moęž‰dowalega, to aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 5.20 \xt Aęž‰fe 5.11\x*Koęž‰sega kalu man mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, kalu nolbaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ kalaba saęž‰laki, digalaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰dakiyoęž‰ tagimaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 21 Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰, giyoęž‰ to we kudu hamanaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ gemoęž‰woęž‰ halale soęž‰loęž‰l. Aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, giyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ moęž‰waęž‰laęž‰saęž‰ndaki, tambomoęž‰woęž‰ man imiloęž‰ ka dimidaęž‰bi.  
\v 22 Giyoęž‰ kalu imilig nowoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ nanog dimaęž‰ki daęž‰feakiyoęž‰, dagiyoęž‰ misaęž‰ waęž‰l amioęž‰ golakiyoęž‰, boęž‰eboęž‰ daęž‰feaęž‰soęž‰bo. Kalu nolbaęž‰loęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ dimidab aęž‰noęž‰, ge i oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰gasa dowaki, manoęž‰ digaloęž‰le kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi.  
\v 23 Ge walafoęž‰ modoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kufoęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ge hoęž‰ndeyoęž‰ nakiyoęž‰, wain hoęž‰n haęž‰luwoęž‰loęž‰ naęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 24 Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ nolbaęž‰ siwaęž‰la dimidaęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ semoęž‰ moęž‰walilaki, mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalaba dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Koęž‰sega kalu noloęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ ililoęž‰ dimidoęž‰woęž‰ woęž‰noęž‰le daęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, tif amioęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib.  
\v 25 Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ gan aumboęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰loęž‰ man nafale dimidaęž‰lab noloęž‰ kalaba dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, tambo baęž‰daęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ man nafale dimidaęž‰lab noloęž‰loęž‰ woęž‰noęž‰le dimidab, koęž‰sega aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib.   
\c 6  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 6.1 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.5\x*Keliso kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ madali nanog dian kalu dowab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ inin boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰ haęž‰g amioęž‰ haęž‰sa dowaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ wi oęž‰liaęž‰ nililoęž‰ man koęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰mogagi saęž‰maęž‰ib.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6.2 \xt File 1.16\x*Madali nanog dian kalu, gili boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwoęž‰ Keliso dowoęž‰lalega, e gao oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ â€śe haęž‰g amioęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰noęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ moęž‰gakiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ ini nanogoęž‰ mada nafa, halale dimidaęž‰bi. Moęž‰woęž‰ kalu i oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰sen aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, nanog halaidoęž‰ gililoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Keliso kalu noloęž‰ asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib.  
\s1 Mole alan asulan manoęž‰ hagugu sioęž‰  
\p To we kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰bi.  
\v 3-5 \x - \xo 6.3-5 \xt Gala 1.6-9\x*\x - \xo 6.3-5 \xt 2Tim 3.8, 4.4, Tait 1.14\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰ manoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ widaki, Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ to man digaloęž‰ widab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰imiloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widalega, kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ asugdoęž‰ma iliki, inin wiyoęž‰ mada kailaki gab. Kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ noęž‰noloęž‰ dofoęž‰liki, to ililoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kegemaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ ili moęž‰moęž‰da saęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰ib. To ililoęž‰ kegoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ man koęž‰liloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na moęž‰moęž‰damaęž‰ib. Man aęž‰noęž‰ we, meselanoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ alobaęž‰danoęž‰, mogagi saęž‰lakiloęž‰ sadaęž‰danoęž‰, bulu kedakiloęž‰ moęž‰dimidab aundoęž‰ to saęž‰lanoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ keganoęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib. Kalu i wemaęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ mogagilaęž‰foęž‰liki, to hendeleyoęž‰ i amioęž‰ moęž‰aęž‰lab. Iyoęž‰ Gode eloęž‰ asulab au domaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, mole alan diaęž‰noęž‰ togoęž‰ aęž‰na dowab aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 6.6 \xt Fili 4.11-12, 1Tim 4.8, Hibu 13.5\x*Koęž‰sega Gode eloęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰naki, haęž‰sa dowan man oęž‰liaęž‰ sagalan man oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ ge amioęž‰ ililoęž‰ aumboęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰, ge kelegoęž‰ nafaleyoęž‰ di oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 6.7 \xt Job 1.21\x*Nioęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wenamiloęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰liab amioęž‰ kelegoęž‰ imilig nowoęž‰ moęž‰diaęž‰ handalowoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ henfeloęž‰ we taęž‰foęž‰ haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ imilig nowoęž‰ mada moęž‰diaęž‰haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 8 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ni amioęž‰ maęž‰n oęž‰liaęž‰ soęž‰g saęž‰gaęž‰lan oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li dowoęž‰lalega, nioęž‰ oęž‰li daęž‰lab aęž‰laęž‰asulumaęž‰niki.  
\v 9 Koęž‰sega, kalu abeyoęž‰ mole alandoęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰ asulab i aęž‰noęž‰, man mogagoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ iyoęž‰ susululaliki, iyoęž‰ dafayoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰wa walalaęž‰lab. Iyoęž‰ babale dowaki, kelegoęž‰ noloęž‰ modoęž‰ meselaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ mogagilab.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 6.10 \xt Aęž‰fe 5.5\x*Mole alandoęž‰ diaęž‰noęž‰ asulan aęž‰noęž‰, man mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ tefoęž‰ oęž‰m. Kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ moleyoęž‰ mada alan asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, ili tilidabuwoęž‰ gola dowaki, haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰ ane koęž‰loęž‰, kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ ininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ daęž‰yaęž‰loęž‰ olan oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ alan di.   
\s1 Timoti e halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki, towoęž‰ sioęž‰  
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 6.11 \xt 2Tim 2.22\x*Koęž‰sega ge Godeyaęž‰noęž‰le dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ anib amioęž‰ moęž‰ege dowakiyoęž‰, man we koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi. Digaloęž‰ manoęž‰loęž‰, Gode eloęž‰ asulab au dimidanoęž‰loęž‰, tilidabu manoęž‰loęž‰, haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan manoęž‰loęž‰, halale kagamaęž‰noęž‰ manoęž‰loęž‰, haęž‰sa dowan manoęž‰ we koęž‰loęž‰, ge aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 6.12 \xt 1Kol 9.25-26, 2Tim 4.7\x*Yaęž‰suwa tilidaęž‰daki, nanogoęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, giyoęž‰ halale nai haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ tiniaęž‰bi. Tamin amioęž‰ ge kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ siwaęž‰la kagayaki, tilidabu giloęž‰woęž‰ imoęž‰ widoęž‰ amioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ge melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimaęž‰ki hoęž‰leli koęž‰loęž‰, ge oęž‰goęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ halale taęž‰lima.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 6.13 \xt Yoęž‰n 18.36-37\x*Gode eyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ tambo melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimiab aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ Fondias Failataęž‰ siwaęž‰la kagayakiyoęž‰, ene tilidabuwoęž‰ kalaba fanda sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ ge to we kudu hamanaęž‰ki gemoęž‰ halale saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l.  
\v 14 Gemoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tambo dinafa kudu haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso Alan eloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ miaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ yasilaęž‰likiyoęž‰, digale kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.   
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 6.15 \xt Kala 17.14\x*Gode eyoęž‰ enedoęž‰ hoęž‰lende daęž‰fe alifaęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, Eyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ iligaęž‰faęž‰ib.  
\q1 Gode iwaluloęž‰woęž‰ inaęž‰li e,  
\q2 Kelegoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ e boęž‰foęž‰lab.  
\q1 Kalu Alanaęž‰, Alandeyoęž‰ E,  
\q2 Misaęž‰ dowoęž‰waęž‰, Misaęž‰ Alandeyoęž‰ E.   
\q1
\v 16 Gode imilig e moęž‰sowan.  
\q2 Gode e ene hoęž‰lena iliki,  
\q2 kalu imilig nowoęž‰ e anib amioęž‰ moęž‰kagamaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰ib.  
\q1 E kalu imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰dan koęž‰loęž‰,  
\q2 tif amioęž‰loęž‰ e moęž‰baęž‰baęž‰ib.  
\q1 Niliyoęž‰ e hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo wabudaki,  
\q2 Ene halaidoęž‰woęž‰ koęž‰ngoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ domaęž‰ib.  
\q1 Hendele oęž‰m.   
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 6.17 \xt Luk 12.20-21\x*Henfeloęž‰ wenamioęž‰ moleyoęž‰ modoęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab kalu aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰kailaęž‰maęž‰ki, giyoęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰bi. Koęž‰sega iyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ boęž‰boęž‰geloęž‰ mogagimaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰namidaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰tili asulaki, Godeyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ tili asulumaęž‰ki widaęž‰bi. Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ sagalemaęž‰kiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nafale koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dimiaęž‰sen.  
\v 18 I amioęž‰ man nafaleyoęž‰ waęž‰litaki, iliyoęž‰ man nafale dimidan aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ modoęž‰ dimidaęž‰meleaęž‰ki, giyoęž‰ widaęž‰bi. Inin kelegoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰kanulu taęž‰liaki, nolboęž‰woęž‰ sagalaęž‰liki dimiaęž‰meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰, giyoęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰bi.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 6.19 \xt Madi 6.20\x*Iliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, a diaęž‰nikiloęž‰ aikoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ gelan aumboęž‰, man nafa dimidan aęž‰noęž‰ tif amioęž‰loęž‰ kelegoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dimidaitakigab. Iliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalega, melaęž‰noęž‰ hendele aęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰le diaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 20 Timoti, ge Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to hendele gemoęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰kiloęž‰ dimi aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa tili dowaęž‰bi. Ge Godeyaęž‰ toma, madali toloęž‰ malolaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ ka taęž‰taęž‰bi. Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰dakiyoęž‰, â€śHendeleâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰asulab koęž‰sega, to aęž‰noęž‰ hendelema koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 6.21 \xt 1Tim 1.6, 2Tim 2.18\x*Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ tili asulakiyoęž‰, tilidabu hendele aęž‰noęž‰ iyoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰nab koęž‰loęž‰, giyoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\p Godeyaęž‰ ene haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ dowaęž‰biyoęž‰.   